Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.58,0:00:03.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在眼中尚觉遥远的将来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.21,0:00:06.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知不觉已经来到面前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.87,0:00:09.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并将迅速地成为回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.13,0:00:11.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.39,0:00:13.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「未来」的表情总是有点不安呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.33,0:00:17.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我们就用笑容去迎接她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.76,0:00:18.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.07,0:00:23.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚前辈 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.76,0:00:25.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 早安啊 灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.28,0:00:28.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…我试穿了制服
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.00,0:00:30.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.91,0:00:32.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 很合适哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.19,0:00:41.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.41,0:00:43.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有事吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.22,0:00:47.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是有点高兴而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.56,0:00:51.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.67,0:00:55.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我也成为正式领航员了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.25,0:00:58.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 嗯 恭喜啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.99,0:01:00.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超级恭喜啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.77,0:01:02.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 就只有这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.26,0:01:04.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不是说这个的时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.99,0:01:07.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚前辈要从领航员业界功成身退
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.78,0:01:08.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.98,0:01:10.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.01,0:01:12.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.98,0:01:18.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隐退的理由不只是那样哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.60,0:01:21.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚前辈好像很久以前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.07,0:01:25.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就被邀请担任凤尾舟协会的常务理事了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.67,0:01:28.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不仅仅局限于亚利亚公司
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.63,0:01:31.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是为了整个水上观光业的将来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.68,0:01:33.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想让她尽一份力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.39,0:01:36.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 就算艾莉西亚前辈再怎么厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.91,0:01:39.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也无法同时兼顾两份工作
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.37,0:01:44.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以好像请他们等到我成为正式领航员以后再说了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.46,0:01:48.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说到结婚 其实我也吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.56,0:01:53.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一定也是在等待我的晋级吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.04,0:01:58.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是我再认真一点的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.54,0:02:03.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 有电话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.91,0:02:05.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.86,0:02:07.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬓子！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.91,0:02:09.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晓先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.48,0:02:13.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听…说艾莉西亚小姐要…要结婚是真的吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.64,0:02:14.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是骗人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.75,0:02:16.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我这是骗人的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.73,0:02:17.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.99,0:02:25.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从早上开始就有一大堆人打电话来问这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.67,0:02:28.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都是在哪里听到传闻的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.85,0:04:16.36,TITLE,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,1000)\pos(433,290)\blur9\be1\fsp2}那个 崭新的开端…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.07,0:04:17.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.96,0:04:19.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.65,0:04:20.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.59,0:04:23.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.87,0:04:27.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我熟悉工作之前 艾莉西亚前辈都会留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.74,0:04:33.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隐退仪式全部都由协会来策划
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.01,0:04:35.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那样啦 灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.98,0:04:37.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的没事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.63,0:04:39.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超级担心你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.41,0:04:43.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 蓝华 爱丽丝 谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.92,0:04:47.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.24,0:04:50.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.60,0:04:54.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.03,0:04:56.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.55,0:05:04.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从知道艾莉西亚前辈要隐退那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.04,0:05:08.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就忙这忙那的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.77,0:05:10.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天都忙得晕头转向
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.99,0:05:15.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 艾莉西亚前辈总是面带笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.60,0:05:19.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天都仍旧和平常一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.19,0:05:29.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间像往常一样流逝着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.88,0:05:31.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥和
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.04,0:05:34.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而又幸福的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.39,0:05:39.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里有艾莉西亚前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.55,0:05:43.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有亚利亚社长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.04,0:05:46.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.44,0:05:51.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.93,0:05:53.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.36,0:06:01.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.69,0:06:03.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个数据是什么来着…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.45,0:06:05.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 艾莉西亚前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.07,0:06:08.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这份文件…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.14,0:06:17.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚前辈…？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.04,0:06:43.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.70,0:06:46.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…有份文件我不太明白…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.11,0:06:48.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到处在找你哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.34,0:06:52.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有客人送花来给我了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.54,0:06:55.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.65,0:06:57.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.23,0:07:04.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家…都不希望艾莉西亚前辈隐退的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.51,0:07:11.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,客人也是…市民也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.90,0:07:13.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家其实都…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.98,0:07:18.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最喜欢艾莉西亚前辈了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.86,0:07:21.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是水之三大精灵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.95,0:07:23.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总是很温柔…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.96,0:07:26.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是大家的白雪公主…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.97,0:07:28.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.44,0:07:32.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以想继续跟你在一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.82,0:07:37.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦…对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.82,0:07:38.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.35,0:07:41.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼泪停不下来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.95,0:07:52.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.02,0:07:58.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.81,0:08:01.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实在很久以前…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.55,0:08:07.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里就已经有能力成为正式领航员了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.83,0:08:09.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.95,0:08:15.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我实在太害怕失去与灯里在一起的这段美好的时光…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.78,0:08:18.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道自己身为前辈必须要振作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.50,0:08:21.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须下定决心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.89,0:08:24.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我每次…每次都办不到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.21,0:08:28.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都因为我太任性
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.11,0:08:30.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.35,0:08:37.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.58,0:08:41.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.75,0:08:49.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太多的事情同时发生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.10,0:08:52.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而这一切又太过幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.71,0:08:55.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是非常值得高兴的啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.21,0:09:00.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.11,0:09:03.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论时间或是空间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.89,0:09:05.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都在不断变化
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.13,0:09:08.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以为自己能够理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.35,0:09:12.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但心中却仍旧充满不安与恐惧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.80,0:09:16.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.00,0:09:23.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并肩走在一起时
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.28,0:09:27.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉大家走的是同一条路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.56,0:09:31.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但其实大家都是不一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.53,0:09:34.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都在探索着属于自己的路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.04,0:09:36.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.32,0:09:40.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走在自己的路上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.80,0:09:41.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来到AQUA
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.11,0:09:44.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与艾莉西亚前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.77,0:09:46.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有大家相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.11,0:09:51.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.90,0:09:54.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还想要与在路的前方的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.34,0:09:57.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家的未来邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.71,0:10:01.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.51,0:10:05.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得用笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.39,0:10:07.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来送走艾莉西亚前辈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.72,0:10:17.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.31,0:10:22.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚利亚社长 今天也要加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.52,0:10:28.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一个预约是庵野波平先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.49,0:10:29.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.51,0:10:37.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来那是邮递员叔叔的名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.13,0:10:39.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.64,0:10:42.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天您不用上班吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.59,0:10:45.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？我已经退休啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.55,0:10:49.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后就在办公室做管理的工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.76,0:10:51.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.14,0:10:54.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长久以来真是辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.49,0:11:01.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.76,0:11:03.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是荞麦茶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.16,0:11:07.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的称号是海蓝宝石吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.16,0:11:07.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(472,440)\fs20}Aquamarine
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.30,0:11:08.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.51,0:11:11.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个好名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.35,0:11:16.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到能坐在成为正式领航员的小妹妹的凤尾舟上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.82,0:11:17.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叔叔很高兴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.61,0:11:21.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不寂寞吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.55,0:11:24.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为一些交接工作的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.52,0:11:26.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚前辈一直都陪着我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.24,0:11:28.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.06,0:11:33.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过…明天的隐退仪式结束以后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.49,0:11:34.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就真的变成一个人了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.32,0:11:36.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.43,0:11:39.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有整个城镇陪着小妹妹你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.22,0:11:42.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.44,0:11:48.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的太好喝了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.88,0:11:52.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后透过邮递员叔叔的介绍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.11,0:11:55.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明天也有客人预约了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.84,0:11:56.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.89,0:12:01.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有几位客人是佛洛林咖啡馆的店长
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.89,0:12:01.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(486,440)\fs20}Caffe Florian
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.25,0:12:07.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和钟楼的管理员先生推荐来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.47,0:12:09.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.03,0:12:10.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.82,0:12:14.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在接受很多人的帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.66,0:12:19.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里的亚利亚公司
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.82,0:12:21.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经开张了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.59,0:12:26.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的…亚利亚公司…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.88,0:12:34.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.38,0:12:37.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 准备好了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.84,0:12:53.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.51,0:12:56.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.35,0:13:58.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.09,0:14:00.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是骗人的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.71,0:14:02.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晓 你在哭吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.65,0:14:06.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是高兴的眼泪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.20,0:14:07.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高兴！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.57,0:15:49.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜你成为正式领航员
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.40,0:15:51.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.89,0:16:25.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.24,0:16:29.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没到下雪的季节啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.80,0:16:30.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.86,0:16:32.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白雪公主啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.96,0:16:36.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.73,0:16:38.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.36,0:16:40.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.01,0:16:42.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.02,0:17:30.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安 亚利亚社长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.93,0:17:44.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.37,0:18:12.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 生奶油可可吗？好久没喝了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.40,0:18:14.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要多多的奶油
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.46,0:18:15.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.28,0:18:18.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雅典娜前辈 超级任性的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.08,0:18:22.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来啦 核桃面包久等啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.75,0:18:24.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是刚刚出炉的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.60,0:18:28.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.50,0:18:30.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.46,0:18:35.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗…在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.76,0:18:40.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,充满了以前的所有…欢乐的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.39,0:18:50.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打开这扇门 是我一天中的第一个工作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.41,0:18:55.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在打开它 平凡的一天就即将开始
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.95,0:18:58.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而这份温馨的光景…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.35,0:19:01.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会被冷冽的晨风吹散
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.30,0:19:04.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.79,0:19:06.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.08,0:19:11.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.13,0:19:13.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将演绎出「现在」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.84,0:19:26.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小爱 之后的大家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.75,0:19:30.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安的说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.93,0:19:32.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空中邮递员伍迪先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.75,0:19:36.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近在上班前都会给我送来新鲜的鸡蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.13,0:19:40.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说他浮岛的家中开始养鸡了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.00,0:19:42.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝华小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.16,0:19:46.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姬屋的年轻分店长 蓝华呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.30,0:19:44.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs26}来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.43,0:19:49.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近开始有了威信 非常地帅哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.35,0:19:52.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过只有我们两个人在的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.83,0:19:55.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是跟以前一样是个爱哭鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.86,0:20:00.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说阿鲁前段时间也成功晋级了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.19,0:20:02.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 托大家的福
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.65,0:20:06.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然最近不怎么见面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.89,0:20:10.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过蓝华都会把他的近况详细地告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.87,0:20:12.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说还长高了一点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.44,0:20:17.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晓先生也成功晋级了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.19,0:20:20.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总是不知不觉出现在店里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.13,0:20:22.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我吓一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.94,0:20:26.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我觉得这一定是晓先生特有的关心方式
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.56,0:20:28.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好像很闲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.94,0:20:29.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.96,0:20:33.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶尔也到浮岛来玩玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.40,0:20:37.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.85,0:20:40.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传说中的跳级正式领航员爱丽丝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.72,0:20:42.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总是成为周围目光的焦点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.45,0:20:47.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而爱丽丝最最热衷的自我原则呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.78,0:20:50.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是三个人一块去玩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.18,0:20:53.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不三个人一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.62,0:20:55.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界就会毁灭掉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.80,0:20:58.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.23,0:21:04.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雅典娜前辈受到大众的推举
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.55,0:21:06.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前段时间终于在歌剧院
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.49,0:21:08.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,召开了一场个人演唱会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.37,0:21:12.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然爱丽丝抱怨她怠慢了领航员的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.21,0:21:16.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过演唱会当天看到雅典娜前辈那身姿却感动到不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.92,0:21:19.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偷偷哭了呢 要保密哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.63,0:21:23.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姬屋的晃前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.36,0:21:24.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在名副其实地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.26,0:21:28.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为了光芒四射的No.1领航员
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.35,0:21:33.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的身姿 真可谓是盛情绽放的蔷薇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.96,0:21:36.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 她总是碍手碍脚的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.38,0:21:39.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定要让我的时代早日到来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.67,0:21:40.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.21,0:21:44.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我知道她心里肯定因为
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.41,0:21:46.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晃前辈的活跃而高兴得不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.80,0:21:49.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.18,0:21:54.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们永远的白雪公主 艾莉西亚前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.41,0:22:01.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忙着出席各式各样的演讲和典礼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.05,0:22:04.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,集会和联欢会等等等等
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.27,0:22:06.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天都忙得不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.13,0:22:14.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前段时间我还看到了她与祖母一起担任特邀讲师
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.91,0:22:21.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 在时间允许的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.77,0:22:23.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日安
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.52,0:22:25.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祖母
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.31,0:22:27.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.23,0:22:30.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们又来看你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.26,0:22:37.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都像这样 跟祖母一起来看我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.68,0:22:42.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟以前一样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.01,0:22:44.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有如水之精灵一般
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.96,0:22:47.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向我们露出美丽的微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.26,0:22:52.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被幸福包围着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.47,0:22:55.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带来许多开端的风
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.92,0:23:00.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果也能送到小爱那里就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.71,0:23:18.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚利亚社长 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.92,0:23:23.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里前辈 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.24,0:23:26.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我试穿了制服…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.98,0:23:33.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎么样呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.82,0:23:36.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 非常好看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.92,0:23:37.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小爱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.01,0:23:55.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.27,0:23:57.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有事吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.38,0:24:08.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.45,0:24:09.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点高兴罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.66,0:24:29.64,END,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(445,469)\bord0\shad1\fsp6\3c&H475B5F&\4c&H575757&}愿那起始之风  吹拂到您身边…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OPJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.56,0:02:37.62,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}憶えていますか？ あの日を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.78,0:02:47.61,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}ふと感じた ときめきを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.65,0:02:57.74,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}蒼い日差し浴びて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.64,0:03:02.14,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}風を切る君に
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.43,0:03:08.87,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}見とれてると 目が合って
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.95,0:03:13.59,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}笑顔こぼれた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.56,0:03:20.71,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}まるで スピラーレ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.83,0:03:27.65,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,1000)\an7}鮮やかに 回り出した日々
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.63,0:03:32.01,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}いつも いつでも
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.38,0:03:37.65,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}愛が満ちていた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.28,0:03:41.92,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}きっと スピラーレ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.33,0:03:51.64,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}あたたかな 毎日を重ねたら
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.13,0:04:00.06,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}いつの間にか 遠くに
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.19,0:04:04.76,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,1000)}来ていたのね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OPCH】
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.56,0:02:37.62,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}可曾记得？ 那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.78,0:02:47.61,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}涌上心头的 感动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.65,0:02:57.74,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}沐浴着湛蓝的阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.64,0:03:02.14,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}你迎风前行的身姿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.43,0:03:08.87,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}让我陶醉时 目光相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.95,0:03:13.59,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我们齐声欢笑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.56,0:03:20.71,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}就像那 小小漩涡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.83,0:03:27.65,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,1000)\an3}炫目光芒中 崭露头角的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.63,0:03:32.01,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}永远地 充满
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.38,0:03:37.65,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}让人陶醉的爱意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.28,0:03:41.92,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}一定如 小小漩涡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.33,0:03:51.64,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}每个温暖的 日子往复着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.13,0:04:00.06,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}不经意间 从那远方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.19,0:04:04.76,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,1000)}来到我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【EDJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.26,0:19:37.15,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}頬をなでる 優しい風
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.89,0:19:46.32,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}波音に 揺られて
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.66,0:19:55.93,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}体の中 ほどけてゆくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.51,0:20:06.69,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}目を閉じて 見えてくる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.30,0:20:14.95,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}風の行く道が
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.19,0:20:25.05,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}さあ 漕ぎ出そう 光る波へ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.37,0:20:34.21,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}笑顏が すぐ こぼれる
